DB Schema

id: INT <unique identifier for the campaign>
pledged: INT <amount pledged so far>
goal: INT <funding target>
currency: STRING <the currency in which the goal is set>
backers: INT <number of people pledging>
deadline: DATE <cutoff date for funding>
media: STRING <image or video link for splash page>
category: STRING <type of campaign (games, music, etc.)>
location: STRING <where the campaign is based>

Kickstarter allows campaigns in:
US 'USD', UK 'GBP', Canada 'CAD', Australia 'AUD', New Zealand 'NZD', the Netherlands 'EUR', Denmark 'DKK', Ireland 'EUR', Norway 'NOK', Sweden 'SEK', Germany 'EUR', France 'EUR', Spain 'EUR', Italy 'EUR', Austria 'EUR', Belgium 'EUR', Switzerland 'CHF', Luxembourg 'EUR', Hong Kong 'HKD', Singapore 'SGD', Mexico 'MXN', and Japan 'JPY'